protos.dispositions.FormattedDisposition.title:
Formatted dispositions. E.g.
  'formatted_dispositions': [
    {
       'dispositions': [
          {'name': 'Child1'},
          {'name': 'Child2', 'usage': 'outbound' },
          {'name': 'Child3', 'usage': 'inbound'}
      ],
      name: name123
    },
   {
       'dispositions': [
          {'name': 'Child4', 'usage': 'outbound' }
      ],
      name: name456,
      usage: outbound
    }
  ]
